{
  "3119540": {
    "name": "缮写室 ：羊皮卷大师",
    "steam_appid": 3119540,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喇叭插在屁股里、长着人脸的马、被天使与百合花环绕的华丽镀金字母——没有人能比中世纪艺术家更有想象力。嘿，说的就是你！欢迎来到你专属的彩绘手稿工坊——《Scriptorium ( 缮写室 ：羊皮卷大师 )》，一个没有计时、没有压力且温馨放松的创作空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>故事模式</strong>中创建你的角色，在充满八卦消息的王国里接受显赫赞助人的委托。绘制战斗与爱情，装饰情书与勒索信，设计地图、假面舞会，或者*咳咳*各种离奇的艺术作品。每一次委托都会让你参与打造一场王室大戏，不亲眼见证是很难相信的。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更偏爱纯粹的创作？在<strong>沙盒模式</strong>中，《Scriptorium ( 缮写室 ：羊皮卷大师 )》将化身为你的中世纪版创作工具平台。空白羊皮纸、完整的中世纪素材库，没有客户也没有委托，只有你自己和无边无际的想象力！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/dafcb3be9f0123181a480d82adcece78.poster.avif?t=1772199229\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/dafcb3be9f0123181a480d82adcece78.webm?t=1772199229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/dafcb3be9f0123181a480d82adcece78.mp4?t=1772199229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/367d010ff6d2df3031342cb0c0694cd3.avif?t=1772199229\" width=1330 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构图界面是缮写室的创作核心，你会在这里决定要以何种方式呈现你的杰作。从多种形状与尺寸的浅色或深色羊皮纸中进行选择，然后将设计元素直接拖放到画布上。使用包含1000+张基于真实中世纪艺术的丰富图库，包括野兽、昆虫、王子、乞丐、面孔、屁股、服饰、表情、植物、零碎物与装饰性边注。使用带有华丽大写字母装饰的中世纪字体添加文字，完成你的彩绘页面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/2a6e2bcf25b39a5e511cab12e86959cf.poster.avif?t=1772199229\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/2a6e2bcf25b39a5e511cab12e86959cf.webm?t=1772199229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/2a6e2bcf25b39a5e511cab12e86959cf.mp4?t=1772199229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/4fe63bceba595696ef3926c2c2a6946c.avif?t=1772199229\" width=1330 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >千奇百怪的客户会带来各种请求，比如蜗牛与骑士的史诗大战，又或者和平、爱情与瘟疫的和谐场景等等……而且这些还不是最怪的。但顾客永远是对的！你的工作就是以自己的风格完成他们的心愿，尽情创作、享受乐趣。让你的艺术传遍王国，成为吟游诗人和史学家传颂数百年的传奇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/4790d209a43c6bdcd5f190bca2f32c27.poster.avif?t=1772199229\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/4790d209a43c6bdcd5f190bca2f32c27.webm?t=1772199229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/4790d209a43c6bdcd5f190bca2f32c27.mp4?t=1772199229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/fdddcdddf246b2950e56d6723781f5ba.avif?t=1772199229\" width=1330 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把你的缮写室打造成王国里最温馨的工坊。用收入装饰你的空间：家具、灯光、挂毯、花卉、窗户、立柱与地毯，再配上一位宠物伙伴，有呼噜作响的猫、忠诚的狗，甚至还有一条小龙，让这里真正成为你的天地。艺术所在即为家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/a3516e755805f426e1ddb9b504c4d257.poster.avif?t=1772199229\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/a3516e755805f426e1ddb9b504c4d257.webm?t=1772199229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/a3516e755805f426e1ddb9b504c4d257.mp4?t=1772199229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/dbf45ff32d5a703afc8e43097fc9b53d.avif?t=1772199229\" width=1330 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满想象力的玩家们已经在《Scriptorium ( 缮写室 ：羊皮卷大师 )》中大展身手，创作出了：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >信件与邀请函</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装饰过的歌词与插画名言</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >塔罗牌</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱的贴纸</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可打印的涂色页</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >桌面壁纸</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奇幻地图</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >桌面角色扮演游戏的道具与手册</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏、电影与流行文化名场面的中世纪再创作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然了，还有梗图！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Scriptorium ( 缮写室 ：羊皮卷大师 )》为分享而建。将作品保存到你的画廊，然后导出为可进行打印与社交分享的.PNG图片。把它分享给全世界，或作为属于你的小小杰作永久珍藏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/76a7c4298843b0d7e122d67e3f342556.poster.avif?t=1772199229\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/76a7c4298843b0d7e122d67e3f342556.webm?t=1772199229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119540/extras/76a7c4298843b0d7e122d67e3f342556.mp4?t=1772199229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>如果你喜欢以下游戏，我们觉得你也一定会爱上《Scriptorium ( 缮写室 ：羊皮卷大师 )》：</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A Little To The Left, Sticky Business, Tiny Glade, Hozy, House Flipper 2, Make Room, Canvas of Kings, Is this seat taken?, Tiny Book Shop, Strange Antiquities, Blender, Wallpaper Engine, Inkulinati, Kingdom Come: Deliverance and Pentiment</i></p>",
